  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.mp4?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The path is not easy:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game challenges every player! Don't give up! The more you lose - the better you become!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You like sakura? No worries, mate! If you're into art, you'll find something here that you'll love! Do you like solving puzzles? - There are loads of them! You like a good boss battle? There are several!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game has 100 levels and several secret ones!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.mp4?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interesting mechanics that will not let you get bored</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various puzzles</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The whole game is black and white</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There are levels on which you can and even need to just relax</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/8153ef5f88235bb692ca7048eb966b3c.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=715 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/8153ef5f88235bb692ca7048eb966b3c.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bleb goes through a breakup with his girlfriend, after which he falls into a dream and now he has a lot of challenges to face! But what happens afterwards?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/a1a8fe51246200297c926a4aef173d66.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/a1a8fe51246200297c926a4aef173d66.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the developer:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game was created by a solo developer.</strong> <i>\"I wanted to make a game where after completing each level, the player can say - OH YEAH I DID IT!\"</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/77e9b6110d4e6cd8b72223150dfd5a7c.mp4?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The path is not easy:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game challenges every player! Don't give up! The more you lose - the better you become!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You like sakura? No worries, mate! If you're into art, you'll find something here that you'll love! Do you like solving puzzles? - There are loads of them! You like a good boss battle? There are several!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game has 100 levels and several secret ones!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/40c2f459a1d1cfeef42329c9b4ab2c6a.mp4?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interesting mechanics that will not let you get bored</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various puzzles</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The whole game is black and white</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There are levels on which you can and even need to just relax</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/8153ef5f88235bb692ca7048eb966b3c.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=715 height=343 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/8153ef5f88235bb692ca7048eb966b3c.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bleb goes through a breakup with his girlfriend, after which he falls into a dream and now he has a lot of challenges to face! But what happens afterwards?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/a1a8fe51246200297c926a4aef173d66.poster.avif?t=1749201367\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081760/extras/a1a8fe51246200297c926a4aef173d66.webm?t=1749201367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the developer:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game was created by a solo developer.</strong> <i>\"I wanted to make a game where after completing each level, the player can say - OH YEAH I DID IT!\"</i></p>",
